<h2>What is Pitch Catchers?</h2>
<p>An app that allows screenwriters to upload and share their elevator pitch they worked so hard for.</p>
<p>Film Industry Agents and Scouts log in everyday and decide which pitch has potential to become a film.</p>
<p>No need to wait for a "promised" interview.</p>
<p>No need to find an agent.</p>
<p>No need to wait and get "discovered".</p>

<p>Pitch Catchers will do everything for you.</p>

